			"relation": "elab-addition"
		},
		{
			"id": 9,
			"parent": 7,
			"text": "Second , we perform joint learning on semantic tense , eventuality type , and modality of an event . <S>",
			"relation": "elab-process_step"
		},
		{
			"id": 10,
